com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record

Class GenericDeviceLocatorRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.SensorRecord
      • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.GenericDeviceLocatorRecord

  • public class GenericDeviceLocatorRecord
extends SensorRecord
    This record is used to store the location and type information for devices on the IPMB or management controller private busses that are neither IPMI FRU devices nor IPMI management controllers.
